org.codice.ddf.registry.identification

Class IdentificationPlugin

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.codice.ddf.registry.identification.IdentificationPlugin
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    PostIngestPlugin, PreIngestPlugin

    public class IdentificationPlugin
extends Object
implements PreIngestPlugin, PostIngestPlugin
    IdentificationPlugin is a Pre/PostIngestPlugin that assigns a localID when a metacard is added to the catalog and an originID to a registry metacard during creation. It also ensures that duplicate registry-ids are not added to the catalog.
